Package uk.co.spudsoft.birt.emitters.excel

Class Summary
ClientAnchorConversions ClientAnchorConversions provides a small set of functions for converting the values used with ClientAnchors.
ExcelEmitter ExcelEmitter is the base class for the two Excel emitters in this bundle.
FontManager FontManager is a cache of fonts to enable POI Fonts to be reused based upon their BIRT styles.
StyleManager StyleManager is a cache of POI CellStyles to enable POI CellStyles to be reused based upon their BIRT styles.
StyleManagerHUtils StyleManagerHUtils is an extension of the StyleManagerUtils to provide HSSFWorkbook specific functionality.
StyleManagerUtils StyleManagerUtils contains methods implementing the details of converting BIRT styles to POI styles.
StyleManagerXUtils StyleManagerXUtils is an extension of the StyleManagerUtils to provide XSSFWorkbook specific functionality.
StyleStack StyleStack maintains a stack of BIRT styles so that can be applied hierarchically to elements.
XlsEmitter XlsEmitter is the leaf class for implementing the ExcelEmitter with HSSFWorkbook.
XlsxEmitter XlsxEmitter is the leaf class for implementing the ExcelEmitter with XSSFWorkbook.
